params.sqlcmd: "SELECT distinct " +" T_QUERY_INFO.\\"EDIT_TYP\\" As \\"EDIT_TYP\\", " +" T_QUERY_INFO.\\"QUERY_NAME\\" As \\"QUERY_NAME\\", " +" T_QUERY_INFO.\\"QUERY_GROUP\\" As \\"QUERY_GROUP\\", " +" T_QUERY_INFO.\\"MEMO\\" As \\"MEMO\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_QUERY_INFO.\\"CREATED_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') As \\"CREATED_DATE\\", " +" T_QUERY_INFO.\\"CREATED_BY\\" As \\"CREATED_BY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_QUERY_INFO.\\"UPDATED_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') As \\"UPDATED_DATE\\", " +" T_QUERY_INFO.\\"UPDATED_BY\\" As \\"UPDATED_BY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_QUERY_INFO.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\") As \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" T_QUERY_INFO.\\"QUERY_CD\\" As \\"QUERY_CD\\", " +" T_QUERY_INFO.\\"SQL_INFO\\" As \\"SQL_INFO\\", " +" T_QUERY_INFO.\\"CREATED_PRG_NM\\" As \\"CREATED_PRG_NM\\", " +" T_QUERY_INFO.\\"UPDATED_PRG_NM\\" As \\"UPDATED_PRG_NM\\" " +"FROM " +" T_QUERY_INFO, " +" BELONG_MST, " +" T_BUSINESS_GROUP_QUERY " +"WHERE " +" BELONG_MST.\\"USER_CD\\" = ? " +" and BELONG_MST.\\"BUSINESS_GROUP_CD\\" = T_BUSINESS_GROUP_QUERY.\\"BUSINESS_GROUP_CD\\" " +" and T_BUSINESS_GROUP_QUERY.\\"QUERY_CD\\" = T_QUERY_INFO.\\"QUERY_CD\\" " +" and T_QUERY_INFO.\\"QUERY_NAME\\" LIKE ? " +" and T_QUERY_INFO.\\"QUERY_GROUP\\" LIKE ? " +" and T_QUERY_INFO.\\"MEMO\\" LIKE ? " +" and T_QUERY_INFO.\\"CREATED_BY\\" = ? " +" and TO_DATE(T_QUERY_INFO.\\"CREATED_DATE\\") >= ? " +" and TO_DATE(T_QUERY_INFO.\\"CREATED_DATE\\") <= ? " +"ORDER BY " +" QUERY_GROUP, " +" QUERY_NAME, " +" MEMO, " +" CREATED_BY, " +" CREATED_DATE"
